                    <div class="p-4 rounded bg-dark border border-light">
                      <figure class="text-center mb-0">
                        <blockquote class="blockquote">
                          <p class="text-muted text-start mb-4" style="line-height: 1.8;">
                            CitySafe is a web-based disaster response app that provides
                            real-time alerts, localized notifications, and reliable information
                            during emergencies. It helps citizens stay informed, empowers them
                            to send SOS requests for immediate assistance, and supports city officials and
                            responders in coordinating relief efforts efficiently.
                          </p>
                          <p class="text-muted text-start mb-0">
                            CitySafe was developed as a <em class="text-primary">capstone research project</em> entitled
                            “CitySafe: Urban Disaster Response App”, with the goal of creating a
                            user-friendly, efficient, and compassionate system that strengthens
                            disaster resilience in urban areas.
                          </p>
                        </blockquote>
                        <figcaption class="blockquote-footer mt-4 mb-0">
                          Capstone Research Project <cite title="Source Title" class="text-primary fw-bold">“CitySafe:
                            Urban Disaster Response App”</cite>
                        </figcaption>
                      </figure>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                </div>

                <div class="col-sm-4">
